The paper explores the characteristics of live social broadcasts on Facebook Live, which involves analyzing data related to network infrastructure, video properties, and social engagement. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Multimedia (cs.MM), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Software Engineering (cs.SD), and Computers and Society (cs.CY). Among these, cs.SI is the most likely category as the paper focuses on social engagement and user-generated content.
